twcore.misc.command
Class CommandDefinition

java.lang.Object
  twcore.misc.command.CommandDefinition

public class CommandDefinition
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
Stefan / Mythrandir commandString example: game String 'Game name' required:Integer 'Time limit' '30':String 'Team 1 name' 'freq 1':String 'Team 2 name' 'freq 2' each commandstring contains the key name and then a list of parameters separated by a ':', following this structure - parameter type (Integer / Double / String). Capitalization of the first letter is obligatory - parameter name enclosed by single quotes (') and then either 'required' specifying that this is a required parameters or another value enclosed by single quotes defining the default value if it's not specified with. currently supported objects: Integer Double String (make sure to use capital letters correctly)
